OL,3,CBME women 'twice as likely to be on
OL,4,Czero-hours contracts as white men'
OL,6,FBME workers ` particularly women ` are
OL,7,Fmore likely to be on the "some of the
OL,8,Fworst contracts, with the worst pay
OL,9,Fand conditions", according to the
OL,10,Funion body.
OL,12,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,13,F"Zero-hours contracts are a nightmare
OL,14,Ffor workers and a dream for bad bosses.
OL,16,F"They hand almost total control over
OL,17,Fhours and earning power to managers,
OL,18,Fmaking it nearly impossible for
OL,19,Fworkers to plan their budgets and
OL,20,Ftheir wider lives.
