OL,3,CBME women 'twice as likely to be on
OL,4,Czero-hours contracts as white men'
OL,6,F"These are some of the worst contracts
OL,7,Faround, and BME women are twice as
OL,8,Flikely to be on these contracts as
OL,9,Fwhite men. That's a prime example of
OL,10,Fstructural racism in action.
OL,12,F"It's time to end the scourge of
OL,13,Finsecure work once and for all,
OL,14,Fstarting with a ban on zero-hours
OL,15,Fcontracts, like Labour is proposing in
OL,16,Fits New Deal for Working People.
OL,18,F"That's how you start to tackle the
OL,19,Fstructural racism that is holding BME
OL,20,Fworkers back."
