OL,6,FA Department for Business and Trade
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Zero-hour
OL,8,Fcontracts offer flexibility for people
OL,9,Fwho may need to balance work around
OL,10,Fpersonal commitments whilst helping
OL,11,Femployers who have less demand for
OL,12,Fpermanent staff.
OL,14,F"At the beginning of this month, the
OL,15,FGovernment increased the National
OL,16,FLiving Wage for workers aged 21 and
OL,17,Fover, putting more money in the
OL,18,Fpockets of almost three million
OL,19,Fworkers."
